originalText: up_yussel
Start Element
yussel
Imbecile!

::You see a serious looking man in an almost blindingly white lab coat. He seems somewhat aggravated - walking in circles, sighing constantly, as if he is expecting something to happen, yet it never does. Once you approach him, he gives you a condescending look before talking.::

What is it now?  Why do the unimportant ones always insist on troubling me. Oh... ::He rubs his forehead.:: Look, I don't have much time to waste on you, you... random... person... so you better be quick about it.
You again...
context.npc_up_yussel_pissedOff
I had some questions I wanted to ask you, if you have the time.
I'll come back later.

If you must... ::He sighs.::

Come on, hurry it up.
context.npc_up_yussel_met
::He raises his voice.:: I beg your pardon!?
Who are you?
Why are you here and what do you know about this place?
What do you know about Tchortists?
So long.
Oh, you know what I'm talking about, you condenscending dirtbag
Well, you think I'm wasting your time. That's not a nice thing to say to someone.
::Turn around and leave.::

Ah, I see now who I'm dealing with. An imbecile! I'm a condenscening bastard? Why? Is it because I'm not willing to babble about unimportant subjects with you! I...

Actually, there is no purpose in this. I'll just say goodbye...

I don't care if you think it's nice or not. I don't owe you anything you imbecile! It's the people like you that disturb me constantly in the most inappropriate moments, which causes me to behave the way I behave! What did you expect to hear? "Welcome stranger! Ask me anything! I have all the time in the world to answer your exasperating questions."
Yes, run away now after you've spoken your childish insult. Get lost! I don't care, you imbecile!
Goodbye!
::He makes a brief pause.:: Actually, just get lost. I'm not wasting my time arguing with you...
